  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>FilterDevice</TypeRef> method removes the specified <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice">IGraphicsDevice</PageRef>
      object from the current filtered device set.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void FilterDevice(IGraphicsDevice* targetDevice);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="IGraphicsDevice*!cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice" Name="targetDevice">
          The device to remove from the filtered device set
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
